  <p>The apparent reduction in the share of General Medical Services Non-Cash Limited expenditure from 1998-99 reflects a transfer of resources from that budget to the Scottish Council for Postgraduate Medical and Dental Education when it took over responsibility for vocational training for GPs.</p>

